Transactions and balances between IEnova and its subsidiaries have been eliminated upon consolidation and are not disclosed in this note, except for those transactions between continued and discontinued operations.

Transactions between continued and discontinued operations are not eliminated in consolidation. Any proﬁt made from sales to external parties by the discontinued operations are presented outside continuing operations.
